        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】Samsung 可卷曲手机    Cling Band 戴手上可感应身体状况</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cling-band</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 07:23:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cling Band]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221882</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">万众瞩目的盛事 MWC 2024 在西班牙巴塞隆拿举行，Samsung 就率先抛出震撼弹，首次展示了可卷曲萤幕的概念手机 Cling Band，同场亦有可调整萤幕视角以保护私隐的 Flex Magic Pixel。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221890" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/bb1iu3qbimg-694x495.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="495" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/bb1iu3qbimg-694x495.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/bb1iu3qbimg.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221883 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/202402281042585fd725-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/202402281042585fd725-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/202402281042585fd725.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可卷曲萤幕的概念手机 Cling Band</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Cling Band 在未卷曲的情况下，基本上如一般手机无异，惟机背有多个板块，这种设计方便用家卷曲手机。更有趣的是，Cling Band 可让用家在卷曲后戴上手上，萤幕在卷曲后大致平顺，少许不平。Cling Band 还能透过内建心率感应器纪录身体活动状况，但现时 Samsung 尚未透露此概念设计具体细节。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了 Cling Band 概念手机外，Samsung 在今年的 MWC 上展示了多款概念手机，包括可调整萤幕视角以保护私隐的 Flex Magic Pixel。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/2408672">TVBS</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/samsung-s24-%e7%8f%be%e5%a0%b4%e6%b8%ac%e8%a9%a6%e9%96%8b%e7%ae%b1%e3%80%80%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-7-%e5%a4%a7%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung S24 现场测试开箱影片　港人最爱 7 大功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/samsung-s24-ultra-first-look/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra　外形　手感　AI 功能　操作体验初步评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/samsung-know-smart-tv-2024/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung Know 再获 CC 认证，今年将扩展至智能电视产品</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/">【MWC 2024】Samsung 可卷曲手机    Cling Band 戴手上可感应身体状况</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
