        <item>
            <title>《FF7 Rebirth》Sony 印碟摆乌龙印错标签，玩家要入「资料碟」来玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 05:30:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FF 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Final Fantasy]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[square enix]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221867</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》在今日正式推出（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/07/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth/game-channel/">相关报道</a>），岂料就在推出前一日，Square Enix 发布紧急公告，表示 SONY 制作过程出错，致使日本版《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》 游戏光碟和数据光碟碟面印刷相反。</p><p>Square Enix 在紧急公告中表示，虽然光碟印刷出错，但已购买了错版光碟的玩家仍可游玩，只是要倒转放入光碟的次序。Square Enix 公告指，拿到错版游戏的玩家需要先将黑色「Play Disc」光碟放入游戏主机，安装游戏内容，跟随指示完成安装后，就可以将白色「Data Disc」放入游戏机游玩。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/8238652320c04b9d6ecf-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/8238652320c04b9d6ecf-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/8238652320c04b9d6ecf.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》早前已推出体验版，官方表示拥有体验版保存资料的玩家，可以于正式版领取「咕波幸运符＆冒险道具套组」。咕波幸运符有一定机率使取得材料道具数量增加的配件；而冒险道具套组有治疗剂和乙太等，由能在冒险中派上用场的道具组成的套组。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2402/28/news181.html?fbclid=IwAR2sXCIehFrI2jHsEaZ4BEmt9h2-t-Rp3I_8zyVXz-Q2izQaesors84ON_I">IT Media News</a>、<a href="https://www.jp.square-enix.com/ffvii_rebirth/news/information/17175.html">Square Enix JP</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/28/final-fantasy-16-echoes-of-the-fallen-reivew/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】《Final Fantasy XVI：Echoes of the Fallen》 历代最强怪物登场+天空古代遗迹探索</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/04/square-enix-ai/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Square Enix 将积极使用 AI 创作，社长：生成式 AI 提高开发效率</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/">《FF7 Rebirth》Sony 印碟摆乌龙印错标签，玩家要入「资料碟」来玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
