        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】劲量 28,000 mAh 超大电智能电话，可待机逾 90 日、通话时间 122 小时</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=energizer-28000-mah-mobile</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Energizer]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221668</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>著名的电池生产商 Energizer（劲量）在 2020 年 MWC 上曾发布过一款待机长达 50 日的手机，今日 Energizer 再创新猷，于 MWC 2024 发布一款电池容量达 28,000mAh 的手机，号称全球最大电池容量的手机，据悉其待机时间长达 94 天。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0349-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0349-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0349.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这部手提电话实际上并非 Energizer 制造，而是由 Avenir Telecom 经 Energizer 授权下使用该品牌推出，型号为 Hard Case P28K。能够称自己为「Hard Case」，顾名思义，这款电话防护等级非常高，达到 IP69。制造商声称 P28K 电源足以使用一星期，方便经常要到野外的人。P28K 额定通话时间为 122 小时，而待机时间则长达 2252 小时，换算约为 94 日。</p><p>除续航力惊人，其充电效率亦非常高。这部电话支援 33W 高速充电，而且据制造商表示，如果使用原厂 36W 充电器的话，将能够在 1.5 小时内充满电。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0342-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0342-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dscf0342.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>不过这部电话的缺点是其机身非常「有份量」，厚度达 27.8 mm，重量更有 570 克，差不多等于 3 部 iPhone 15 。除了机身厚重之外，其规格亦比较阳春。P28K 使用 MediaTek MT6789 核心，配备 8GB RAM，256 GB 储存，其萤幕则是 6.78 吋 1080p LCD 萤幕。</p><p>Avenir Telecom 计划在今年 10 月推出这部电话，初步定价为 249.99 欧罗（约港币 2,122.78 元），据悉这部电话将会在美国以外的市场推出。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/25/24082954/avenir-telecom-energizer-hard-case-p28k-28000mah-smartphone">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/apple-working-on-beats-solo-4-headphones/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 推出 iOS 17.4RC 版，揭 Beats Solo 4 正在开发中</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/apple-car-plan-ends/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 电动车计划寿终正寝   2,000 名员工受影响</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone FineWoven 保护套被外媒批评，容易褪色甩皮状况如烂香蕉</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/">【MWC 2024】劲量 28,000 mAh 超大电智能电话，可待机逾 90 日、通话时间 122 小时</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/energizer-28000-mah-mobile/mobile-phone/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼镜加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼镜开会即总结会议要点</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=oppo-air-glasses</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:53:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[oppo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[OPPO Air Glass 3 XR]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221787</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OPPO 近日在世界流动通讯大会（Mobile World Congress，MWC）发布全新「辅助实境智能眼镜」OPPO Air Glass 3 概念产品，据官方资料显示，OPPO Air Glass 3 能够利用手机专属 App 使用 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3，图片来源：OPPO</p><p>OPPO 表示，Air Glass 3 XR 现阶段属概念产品，重量仅在 50g 左右，采用 OPPO 自主研发的树脂晶圆衍射光波导镜片，折射率高达 1.70，显示亮度均匀性大于 50%，入眼峰值亮度超过 1000 尼特。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO 示范影片可见， Air Glass 3 XR 能显示不少资讯</p><p>OPPO 官方表示，使用者可利用手机里的 OPPO Air Glass 3 专属应用程式，开启旗下自主研发的 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 专属应用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲轻触眼镜的镜臂就能够使用语音助理功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 XR 实际佩戴</p><p style="text-align: left;">虽然 OPPO 这款 XR 眼镜看起来非常高科技，而且官方示范影片里面出现的功能亦很实用，OPPO 方面尚未透露 Air Glass 3 XR 上市时间表，因此就让我们拭目以待吧。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_28703"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SedimxtA73g?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: left;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.oppo.com/cn/newsroom/press/514/">OPPO</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SedimxtA73g">Oppo@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/06/oppo-find-n3-flip-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】OPPO Find N3 Flip　外形　手感　铰位　功能　屏幕　相机　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/nokia-and-oppo-sign-crosslicense-5g-patent-agreement/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OPPO 与 Nokia 签订专利交叉授权，终止长达两年诉讼战</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/">【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼镜加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼镜开会即总结会议要点</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
